{"id": 1218, "genre": 1001, "title": "这年头，你有哪些关于听歌的习惯？", "description": "磁带、CD什么的，目前的主要作用是暴露年龄。（题图来自：James Heimer）", "record_count": 4167, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201609130114476T7qlOLvhEz3DdGB.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-09-14T17:00:36Z", "options": [{"id": 115968, "content": "现在只有在音乐节目上才能发现好听的歌曲", "image": "img/option/option/20160915114241sUAWo1L4xvlf87NJ.jpg", "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 758723}, {"id": 116224, "content": "用echo回声，看评论", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 751122}, {"id": 116225, "content": "网易比联盟好玩", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 307466}, {"id": 116737, "content": "单曲循环以及网易相似推荐", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 717015}, {"id": 116482, "content": "就算是军训时期下载的强军之歌也不会删除", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 693970}, {"id": 117250, "content": "网易云的推荐挺不错", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 761833}, {"id": 116227, "content": "先听开头，再跳到中间高潮，喜欢就收藏，然后下一首", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 412523}, {"id": 116228, "content": "喜欢蓝调音乐，和一些影视原声", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 755672}, {"id": 123140, "content": "怀旧，一首歌听到腻再换", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 792089}, {"id": 137477, "content": "网易云音乐", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 689742}, {"id": 116229, "content": "最近只用Apple Music", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 403001}, {"id": 115974, "content": "let it go", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 298191}, {"id": 116230, "content": "喜欢的歌词会作成漂亮的长图分享出去?。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 572599}, {"id": 116998, "content": "用豆瓣听歌，与好音乐不期而遇", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 753922}, {"id": 115975, "content": "随机播放", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 757239}, {"id": 116231, "content": "以前只听喜欢的歌，现在随机都是喜欢的歌。给网易", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 759387}, {"id": 115976, "content": "听虾米音乐", "image": null, "praise_count": 34, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 683756}, {"id": 116232, "content": "喜欢用蓝牙耳机", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 121726}, {"id": 116488, "content": "周杰伦。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 759830}, {"id": 115977, "content": "听一首歌听到吐 换一首继续单曲循环", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 725392}, {"id": 116233, "content": "一边听歌，一边写作业", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 756697}, {"id": 116745, "content": "网易云音乐\n小众英音的天堂", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 517906}, {"id": 117513, "content": "喜欢用耳机听歌，不喜欢单曲循环，喜欢一个人静静的听", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 763498}, {"id": 115978, "content": "心情差时不听歌", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 758736}, {"id": 116234, "content": "两个软件同时放一首歌::>_<::", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 725463}, {"id": 118794, "content": "隨機播放", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 148630}, {"id": 115979, "content": "网易云", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 758743}, {"id": 116235, "content": "建个夹，里面全是最近超爱的歌", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 751780}, {"id": 116491, "content": "在家用蓝牙小音箱，出门用蓝牙运动耳机。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 725205}, {"id": 117003, "content": "不停地通过各种途径找能感动自己的歌。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 760896}, {"id": 116236, "content": "一定要确保每首歌有它正确的专辑封面；同一个歌手的名字一定大小写，繁简体一模一样；专辑名称会重新编辑，有自己的固定格式。遇到电台节选或者节目上演唱的歌曲剪辑，会自己给它们挑封面。依然坚持用P3听歌。\n´ㅅ｀", "image": "img/option/option/20160915234629tzOcoJFWGURuV1yb.jpg", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 522021}, {"id": 116492, "content": "虾米和酷我", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 179481}, {"id": 117004, "content": "只在车里听歌，空间独立，不会打扰他人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 760899}, {"id": 125708, "content": "CD狗 专辑狗 封面狗 老歌狗 shuffle没爱 单曲循环 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 802088}, {"id": 116237, "content": "喜欢听老歌，新歌听的越来越少", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 741425}, {"id": 119565, "content": "某男生唱过的歌 一直循环播放着", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 773552}, {"id": 115982, "content": "写论文做项目看reading一定会开电脑放音乐", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 514338}, {"id": 116238, "content": "听歌要么单曲循环到厌，要么随机播放一直切。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 753032}, {"id": 116494, "content": "越来越喜欢老歌", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 759409}, {"id": 115983, "content": "用网易云呐！用了它之后看着下面的评论会觉得每一首歌都很有故事，大家的评论让一首歌有了超出于它自身表达的情感，很奇妙", "image": null, "praise_count": 126, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 758751}, {"id": 116239, "content": "看网易云音乐的评论", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 757072}, {"id": 115984, "content": "按地理分歌单，尤爱六十年的傻白甜", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 737191}, {"id": 116240, "content": "不看歌词，故意听不清歌词，不想被歌词带走?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 715493}, {"id": 116752, "content": "网易云最爱   喜欢变听歌边看评论 ，评论就像这歌的故事。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 238715}, {"id": 115985, "content": "网易云音乐  小清新聚集地", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 758762}, {"id": 116241, "content": "手机各种风格的曲子都有，带歌词的，不带歌词的，摇滚，轻音乐…", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 704659}, {"id": 116753, "content": "被各种趣味的歌单吸引，随机收藏几首感脚不错的歌", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 605591}, {"id": 118801, "content": "身边没有同样风格口味的音乐人，比如喜欢重金属，摇滚，乡村，爵士，古典，甚至黑暗，死亡类…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 769514}, {"id": 115986, "content": "必須網易雲呀", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 758763}, {"id": 116242, "content": "有时候会把MD拿出来，听听自己录的歌曲", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 247017}]}